# Social Network Ads Purchase Prediction using Logistic Regression
Project Description


This project predicts whether a user will purchase a product based on Age and Estimated Salary. The dataset is stored in MySQL, fetched using Pandas, trained using Logistic Regression, and deployed using Flask API.

# Technologies Used
Python
MySQL
Pandas
NumPy
Scikit-Learn
Flask
Joblib
Postman

# Project Workflow
CSV Dataset
    ↓
MySQL Database
    ↓
Pandas DataFrame
    ↓
Logistic Regression
    ↓
model.pkl
    ↓
Flask API
    ↓
Postman Testing

# Database Details
Database Name:
CREATE DATABASE social_network;
